{"tid":655133,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4] Monster Hunter World(209) 乜人都冇","createTime":"2018-05-06T08:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T08:52:43.000Z","uid":25195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"38f6f86101596d41237d648ee903555ebfd328e5","tid":655133,"uid":25195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T08:52:06.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.mhchinese.wiki\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhchinese.wiki&d=YAZ%2BkElEEF8wD3E%2BJLjm8AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=b780ea6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mhchinese.wiki</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.monsterhunterworld.com/images/share.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.monsterhunterworld.com%2Fimages%2Fshare.png&h=c727d2a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>網上獵人經驗心得</strong></ins><br />\n<strong>Monster Hunter World官網</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://game.capcom.com/manual/MHW/zh-hant/ps4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgame.capcom.com%2Fmanual%2FMHW%2Fzh-hant%2Fps4&d=YAZ%2BkElEEF8wD3E%2BJLjm8AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=e113691d\" target=\"_blank\">http://game.capcom.com/manual/MHW/zh-hant/ps4</a><br />\n<strong>中文網站教學</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mhchinese.wiki\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhchinese.wiki&d=YAZ%2BkElEEF8wD3E%2BJLjm8AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=b780ea6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mhchinese.wiki</a><br />\n<strong>日本網站教學</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://game8.jp/mhw/196165\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgame8.jp%2Fmhw%2F196165&d=YAZ%2BkElEEF8wD3E%2BJLjm8AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=317e1c1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://game8.jp/mhw/196165</a><br />\n<strong>台灣網站教學</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=5786&amp;page=&amp;snA=136459&amp;last=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D5786%26page%3D%26snA%3D136459%26last%3D&d=YAZ%2BkElEEF8wD3E%2BJLjm8AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=d0a35855\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=5786&amp;page=&amp;snA=136459&amp;last=</a><br />\n<strong>香港資料庫by連登巴打</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1HJRS-3gzioCFp4JF1XH6xzRqExilsm_Ji78T6gQQJ7s/edit#gid=1135373004\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1HJRS-3gzioCFp4JF1XH6xzRqExilsm_Ji78T6gQQJ7s%2Fedit%23gid%3D1135373004&d=YAZ%2BkElEEF8wD3E%2BJLjm8AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=c90f4948\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1HJRS-3gzioCFp4JF1XH6xzRqExilsm_Ji78T6gQQJ7s/edit#gid=1135373004</a><br />\n<strong>配裝模擬器 Skill simulator (日本語)</strong><br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://mhki-db.com/sim/[/urlw.wiki-db.com/sim/[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmhki-db.com%2Fsim%2F%5B%2Furlw.wiki-db.com%2Fsim%2F%5B%2Furl%5D&d=YAZ%2BkElEEF8wD3E%2BJLjm8AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=49c672c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://mhki-db.com/sim/[/urlw.wiki-db.com/sim/[/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>***新手獵人Q&amp;A***</strong></div><br />\n<strong><ins>Q：玩咩武器好？</ins></strong><br />\nA：去鍛練場試手感，獵人冇廢裝。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：一開始用咩裝好？</ins></strong><br />\nA：下位睇防禦力就可以，一係就飛雷龍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：玩男角定女角？</ins></strong><br />\nA：只有外觀分別。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點搵集會區域號碼？</ins></strong><br />\nA：禁option之後禁三角<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：咩武器高輸出？</ins></strong><br />\nA：十隻手指各有長短，用剋屬就可以。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：有無人開個新手群？</ins></strong><br />\nA：冇，有嘢請直接問。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點解連唔到線？</ins></strong><br />\nA：因為要俾錢買PS Plus。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：PC版幾時出？</ins></strong><br />\nA：預計2018秋季出。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：噴血少左點算好？</ins></strong><br />\nA：買個紅色鏡片眼鏡試吓。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：傷害數字可唔可以整走？</ins></strong><br />\nA：設定有得整走。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：鎖定有冇得用3DS果種？</ins></strong><br />\nA：設定有得整。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點解入唔到某啲朋友開嘅任？</ins></strong><br />\nA：低進度入唔到高進度個任，要先觸發劇情，搵到見到條龍，可以發出SOS訊號既位，之後quit任再重開就可以一齊玩。亦都可以等低進度果個睇完cut scene，其他朋友就可以係外面任務板join番。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：特典邊度拎？</ins></strong><br />\nA：係屋仔問管家貓。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：開左角色之後,可唔可以重設?改唔改到名？</ins></strong><br />\nA：請再開多過角色。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：設置地的營區喺邊？</ins></strong><br />\nA：地圖右上方。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：再開新角色，之前beta報酬同特典有冇得再拎？</ins></strong><br />\nA：有巴打試過有。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：冇香港PSN，係咪要買多次？</ins></strong><br />\nA：唔需要，可以開個香港account set常用ps4就可以用有買嘅account玩。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：連線打同solo打有咩分別？</ins></strong><br />\nA：連線會變2.6倍血（網上流傳），所以連線最好齊人。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：我想問某種素材點有？</ins></strong><br />\nA：獵人嘅萬能圖鑑可以幫到你，再唔係問埋個位係農場旁邊位師傅睇睇。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點解用網捉唔到龍？</ins></strong><br />\nA：請盡快做完自由任完成新手教學。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：啲調查任點出架，仲有邊到開架？</ins></strong><br />\nA：調查任係打完隻怪就會出（細怪都會），而開任就要先去1樓調查資源管理所登錄任務，每個任都有金、銀或者銅嘅特別獎勵。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：雌火龍???個任點做?</ins></strong><br />\nA：周圍探索搵雌火痕跡，夠一半佢會叫你返去打一隻蠻顎，打完搵埋剩返果半，儲夠就開櫻火。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：咁搵啲痕跡有無得快d既方法?</ins></strong><br />\nA：有，佢出既位其實得幾個點，你自己記得左，搵完無即退任重開。當然你要先入一次記低。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：Juno係咩?</ins></strong><br />\nA：滅燼龍，你試下連續讀100次，愈讀愈快就會知。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點開麒麟任？</ins></strong><br />\nA：係你打完下位風漂龍之後，去生物學者個邊接自由任。第一個自由任係兩星嘅捕捉搔鳥，打完再返去生物學者接下一個自由任。跟住重覆步驟，捉土砂龍，浮空龍。直到捉埋慘爪龍，就接到個麒麟任。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：咁上位嘅麒麟任呢？</ins></strong><br />\nA：主線打完古龍之後去珊瑚台地8區同12區到搵佢啲痕跡，搵到某個程度就開比你。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：500萬道具包點拎</ins></strong><br />\nA：去小屋個管家禁追加內容，無嘅話就等多陣再搵，個活動壞壞地。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：上下位/ab混裝出唔出到套裝技</ins></strong><br />\nA：可以<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點解唔整TG GP</ins></strong><br />\nA：因為無必要，有咩想問有怪想打，係呢度出句聲，大把巴絲打答你幫你。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：激運劵滿左點算？</ins></strong><br />\nA：手持5張激運劵再攞每日登入獎勵就會激運劵變飯劵，所以想繼續激運就請先用左佢。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins></ins></strong><br />\nSample link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-xgyuX-_B9iQTd-y93sRyI_zIcOocYJa3zMf1HpvbZw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1-xgyuX-_B9iQTd-y93sRyI_zIcOocYJa3zMf1HpvbZw&d=YAZ%2BkElEEF8wD3E%2BJLjm8AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=0a6b5048\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-xgyuX-_B9iQTd-y93sRyI_zIcOocYJa3zMf1HpvbZw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#2<br />\n貓技能YOUTUBE<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qDXkSqEzQks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqDXkSqEzQks&d=YAZ%2BkElEEF8wD3E%2BJLjm8AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=26729904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qDXkSqEzQks</a> <br />\n貓技能文字版<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=5786&amp;snA=136299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D5786%26snA%3D136299&d=YAZ%2BkElEEF8wD3E%2BJLjm8AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=02bf1e85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=5786&amp;snA=136299</a><br />\n<br />\n有Q&amp;A/想係個POST加野嘅人入依條LINK<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/13M9_SV4Q0Jjxp_3em5_O5qu6bNuomVzKASHBoy7QZgQ/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F13M9_SV4Q0Jjxp_3em5_O5qu6bNuomVzKASHBoy7QZgQ%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=YAZ%2BkElEEF8wD3E%2BJLjm8AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=50bbefa6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/13M9_SV4Q0Jjxp_3em5_O5qu6bNuomVzKASHBoy7QZgQ/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"d08020460e9d05bd35110e67c851ac89d8f5200a","tid":655133,"uid":173540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T08:52:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e5ad8330fb1281651ce61b10e745a697677f68","tid":655133,"uid":173540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"